{"tid":1678613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"手足召喚神獸嗰陣千其千其唔好做做呢樣嘢！！！","createTime":"2019-10-27T17:36:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T18:00:22.000Z","uid":176027,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"435521677229b3902af53271525b0664e241f6a0","tid":1678613,"uid":176027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:36:00.000Z","msg":"成日見到手足召喚神獸 熱情招待藍屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一般就用遮&amp;腳幫藍屍做全身按摩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲藍屍流左幾滴鼻血 降血壓血脂之後<br />\n又好快企得返起身 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有啲仲好好彩咁有幾廿萬落袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我在此對各位叫停嘅左膠及善良嘅神獸手足公開表示做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我希望在此提醒各位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為咗藍絲可以安安全全回家 下次再出嚟影手足大頭/攞把刀出嚟斬人/揸車撞到人終身殘廢<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">千祈唔好再升級啦！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1qKEdg1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1qKEdg1.png&h=361f01d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家知老人家骨頭脆 關節鬆㗎啦！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個唔覺意大力左 搞到佢哋斷手斷腳就唔好啦！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">記住千祈唔好啊<br />\n否則真係對唔住犧牲左嘅手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"3fb3a42e2d0bfc57c1ea8d9ed7516062c3173a22","tid":1678613,"uid":176027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:38:03.000Z","msg":"1102維園見"},{"pid":"d512d32bf069ca48f9f0a466dc2846e20bb4aa2c","tid":1678613,"uid":176027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:39:28.000Z","msg":"1102維園"},{"pid":"3e06787efb0db229aab798d7c7474eb8b3e91bf2","tid":1678613,"uid":176027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:39:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a8c70db407cc8c56314fe6d8fe344f2504fd185","tid":1678613,"uid":176027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:40:02.000Z","msg":"1102"},{"pid":"85bdae768f814432b63846ba0ed8df2be037eff4","tid":1678613,"uid":199532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:40:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6d8dbc91ce50fb2380369bd1670c768d4b4bb8b","tid":1678613,"uid":176027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:40:44.000Z","msg":"香港人真係好撚善良"},{"pid":"e4203ac839f2d8257553db50c3e9a1514665c755","tid":1678613,"uid":176027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:41:47.000Z","msg":"推到俾班神獸手足睇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0758bbb437d5cedeb31486f65b8aaa67b9851904","tid":1678613,"uid":5801,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:42:35.000Z","msg":"打機都分打擊技同關節技<br />\n應該要學多幾種攻擊技能先夠全面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25031e50be0494af5456b1f204951bf21aa62428","tid":1678613,"uid":176027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:42:37.000Z","msg":"831 721"},{"pid":"ec9b9ef690c33663776c4567f5da19d2e7147508","tid":1678613,"uid":176027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0758bbb437d5cedeb31486f65b8aaa67b9851904","tid":1678613,"uid":5801,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:42:35.000Z","msg":"打機都分打擊技同關節技<br />\n應該要學多幾種攻擊技能先夠全面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:44:09.000Z","msg":"手足對藍屍手下留情<br />\n但對家係唔會對手足手下留情"},{"pid